title: BIP 61: Emissions for the transition period before Convex Setts Launch
body:
This snapshot vote affects only one suggestion made in the [BIP 61](https://forum.badger.finance/t/bip-61-emissions-12-week-liquidity-mining-program/4767): to continue the emissions at the current week's schedule until the Convex Setts Launch.

Vote:
Keep this week's emission schedule until the Convex Setts Launch?
